description: This file is a C header file defining interfaces and function prototypes for the Beep Master Host Object (BEEP_MHO). It includes licensing information, header guards, and declarations for functions related to creating, removing, enrolling, and initializing the master host object, which are used internally within the Beep component.

methods.name: BeepCreateMasterHost
methods.description: Creates and returns a new instance of the Beep Master Host object.

methods.name: BeepMhoCreate
methods.description: Creates and initializes a new Beep Master Host object.

methods.name: BeepMhoRemove
methods.description: Removes or deallocates the Beep Master Host object.

methods.name: BeepMhoEnrollObjects
methods.description: Enrolls necessary internal objects for the Beep Master Host.

methods.name: BeepMhoInitialize
methods.description: Initializes the Beep Master Host object.
